welcome_message_body: "Welcome to East Renton Highlands, a charming city known for its stunning natural beauty and friendly community. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves primarily Alaska Airlines flights.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves international flights and some domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves as the primary hub for all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for general aviation and private aircraft operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Industrial Airport houses all of the airport's amenities and services, including check-in counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Industrial Airport is responsible for handling all cargo shipments, including freight and mail.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for passengers to use.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport houses all commercial flights and amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves as a hub for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.
